CARBON CO., UTAH UTGenWeb

Carbon County Surnames

This surname database is for people who resided in Carbon County before 1930's. If you would like to contribute names to the surname list send the names of your Carbon County ancestors last name, the town they resided in and your e-mail address. Send your information to Kathy Hamaker.
